This example is an improvement over dummy2.
When click File->Hello, a dialog pops up. Click OK. A greeting will be print out in the terminal, and the name will show up in the list box.

To run:
 
  1. install luban
  2. cd into this directory
  3. ./Dummy.py

Choose File->Hello, there will be a dialog. Click OK will print out a greeting.

Widgets:
  - menus
  - splitter
  - panel
  - sizer
  - text
  - listbox
  - dialog
  - button
  - textfield


